    <h1>Custom Training</h1>

    <div class="section">
      <p>Custom training is available anywhere in the world. We offer any of our
      existing classes on Ruby, Rails, SQL, or Web Design and will customize
      the curriculum to meet your needs.</p>

      <h3 id="pricing">Pricing</h3>

      <p>Pricing is based on the days of instruction and the number of attendees
      in the course. The “Daily Rate” covers the <strong>first six attendees</strong>.</p>

      <table class="centered">
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
